# SwiftFormat configuration for Kudos.
#
# Kept deliberately conservative so it largely agrees with the existing code —
# running `swiftformat AO3_App_OpenSource` should make only small, safe changes,
# not a wholesale reflow. It is advisory (a convenience formatter), not a CI gate.
# No bulk reformat has been run. Apply opportunistically via `Scripts/lint.sh --fix`.

--swiftversion 6.0

--indent 4
--ifdef no-indent
--self remove
--commas inline
--trimwhitespace always

# Line wrapping is intentionally NOT enforced (the codebase wraps by hand), and a
# few rules are disabled to avoid noisy or SwiftUI-unfriendly rewrites.
--disable wrap, wrapArguments, wrapMultilineStatementBraces, redundantClosure, blankLinesAtStartOfScope

--exclude build,build-mac,.build,DerivedData
